metadata.name: Metal and Flower #1
metadata.description:
Metal falls on our heads every day. Our cities, fields and gardens are dotted with it.  The events of spring 2022 in our country prompted the idea of creating a collection of experiments with metal and flowers. Bizarre forms of torn metal sheets in nature's embrace, stems and buds breaking through round holes, shiny needles sticking out through flowers - there is a large field for experimentation. 
1/1 Edition
4724x7098 pxl
300 dpi
Film - Cinestill800
